reviews.review_text: worth hearing Everyone always has a different take on each GD show, but I really think this one is worth listening to, with plenty of juice along the way. The first few songs are a bit rusty but then, I think, it finds its stride. See for yourself at least.
This was my first show! Don't remember much of it :) but I do remember rockin' to Ship of Fools. RIP Jerry.
